{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"cc40fb79-f242-4a4c-922b-9ec382b2456d","content":"There's no pipeline file in this directory, so here's the general migration guidance:\n\n### Replace `VSTest@3` with `dotnet test`\n\n**Before (VSTest@3):**\n```yaml\n- task: VSTest@3\n  inputs:\n    testAssemblyVer2: '**\\*Tests.dll'\n    resultsFolder: $(Agent.TempDirectory)\\TestResults\n    codeCoverageEnabled: true\n```\n\n**After (Microsoft.Testing.Platform via `dotnet test`):**\n```yaml\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: test\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >-\n      --configuration $(BuildConfiguration)\n      --logger \"trx;LogFileName=results.trx\"\n      --collect \"Code Coverage\"\n      --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish test results'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: VSTest\n    testResultsFiles: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.trx'\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish code coverage'\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n### Project changes required\n\nIn each test `.csproj`, enable the new platform:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n  <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### Key differences from VSTest@3\n\n| Concern | VSTest@3 | Microsoft.Testing.Platform |\n|---|---|---|\n| Test runner | `vstest.console.exe` | Built into test binary |\n| Invocation | `VSTest@3` task | `dotnet test` / `DotNetCoreCLI@2` |\n| TRX reports | Built-in | `--logger trx` argument |\n| Code coverage | `codeCoverageEnabled` | `--collect \"Code Coverage\"` |\n| Result publish | Automatic | Separate `PublishTestResults@2` step |\n\nThe `condition: always()` on `PublishTestResults@2` ensures results are published even when tests fail.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"bc6b9e6e-d7f3-4d5b-88bb-0d74c260c4c8","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The directory appears to be empty. This is a general knowledge question about migrating from VSTest@3 to Microsoft.Testing.Platform in Azure DevOps CI pipelines. Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":662,"requestId":"A02A:2C9D9E:BE1D81:DE8D19:69FE85BE"},"id":"68c14ab3-b08a-4bae-b727-428871f77d13","timestamp":"2026-05-09T00:54:36.967Z","parentId":"53a5dad3-9f5e-4c2e-877b-014e52113f28"}
